<topic id='business_definition_justice_organisation.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Justice Organisation - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisation</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisation</xref>
 provides 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 or facilities for persons who are detained for any period of more than 6 hours.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisations</xref>
 were under the jurisdiction of the Home Office or the Justice Department. The responsibility for care delivered in 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisation</xref>
 has been transferred to the NHS.  </p>
  <p>
For the purposes of the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/organisation_data_service.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Organisation_Data_Service</xref>
 code set, 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisations</xref>
 include:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_court">Courts</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_immigration_removal_centre">Immigration Removal Centres</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_police_constabulary">Police Constabularies</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_police_custody_suite">Police Custody Suites</xref>
      </li>
      <li>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_secure_children_s_home">Secure Children's Homes</xref>
      </li>
      <li>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_secure_training_centre">Secure Training Centres</xref>
      </li>
      <li>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">Sexual Assault Referral Centres</xref>
         <p> **</p>
      </li>
      <li>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution">Young Offender Institutions</xref>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
** Note: People are not detained in 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">Sexual Assault Referral Centres</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">SARC</xref>
s), but 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">SARC</xref>
s are included with the other 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisations</xref>
 for the purpose of the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/organisation_data_service.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Organisation_Data_Service</xref>
 file publication.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisations</xref>
, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/commissioning/health-just/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Health and Justice</xref>
.  </p>

